{
  "$schema": "./visual-claims.schema.md",
  "description": "Task-12 (overlay suite) visual-claims manifest. Registered as a SEPARATE per-task manifest (not appended into the shared visual-claims.json) to avoid the shared-file merge hazard while other Wave-2 tasks run in parallel. Each claim binds a neo overlay frame as a complete triplet (.ans via tmux capture-pane -e in session ulw-qa-t12 + .html + cell-grid .json from qa/xterm-render.mjs) with grid-based assertions verifying grok layout + exact palette hexes: accent-blue #7aa2f7 selection/prompt, green #9ece6a favorite/✓/on, red #f7768e auth-missing, dim #6c6c6c, yellow #e0af68 label, border #505058, base bg #141414 — all drawn from .omo/research/neo-grok/ansi-colors.md. Also covers the failure edges (zero models, empty sessions dir, delete-confirm) and the 256-color no-truecolor fallback. Triplet paths are relative to this file's directory (packages/neo/qa). Verify with: node packages/neo/qa/xterm-render.mjs verify-manifest packages/neo/qa/visual-claims-task12.json",
